CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775909467
OL,3,CZoo sees birth of otter triplets from
OL,4,Cone of world's most endangered species
OL,6,FThere are an estimated 5,000 giant
OL,7,Fotters left in the wild, as a result
OL,8,Fof water pollution and hunting, and
OL,9,Fthe trio - two males and a female -
OL,10,Fare the first of their kind to be born
OL,11,Fat the zoo in several years.
OL,13,FAssistant Team Manager of carnivores,
OL,14,FRachael Boatwright, said: "The arrival
OL,15,Fof these three giant otter pups is a
OL,16,Fhugely special moment and marks the
OL,17,Ffirst time the species has been born
OL,18,Fhere in seven years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775909467
OL,3,CZoo sees birth of otter triplets from
OL,4,Cone of world's most endangered species
OL,6,F"The pups recently had their very
OL,7,Ffirst health check-up at eight weeks
OL,8,Fold, where they were weighed and had
OL,9,Ftheir heart, teeth and overall
OL,10,Fcondition assessed by the zoo's vets.
OL,11,FWe're delighted to confirm that all
OL,12,Fthree are healthy and thriving - and
OL,13,Fthat we have two males and one female
OL,14,Fpup.
OL,16,F"At eight-weeks-old, the pups will now
OL,17,Fstart to venture outside alongside
OL,18,Fparents Bonita and Manu, who will
OL,19,Fstart introducing them to the water
OL,20,Fand all of the essential skills
OL,21,Fthey'll need as they grow."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
