PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775909467
OL,3,CZoo sees birth of otter triplets from
OL,4,Cone of world's most endangered species
OL,6,FGiant otters are the world's largest
OL,7,Fspecies of otter, and but
OL,8,Fdeforestation, water pollution and
OL,9,Fillegal hunting has seen a decline in
OL,10,Fnumbers.
OL,12,FThe species is listed by the
OL,13,FInternational Union for the
OL,14,FConservation of Nature (IUCN), meaning
OL,15,Fit faces a very high risk of
OL,16,Fextinction without urgent conservation
OL,17,Faction.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775909467
OL,3,CZoo sees birth of otter triplets from
OL,4,Cone of world's most endangered species
OL,6,FKirsten Pullen, Chief Conservation
OL,7,FOfficer at the Zoo, said: "Every birth
OL,8,Frepresents genuine hope for this
OL,9,Fhighly endangered species, and these
OL,10,Fthree giant otter pups are an
OL,11,Fimportant reminder of what
OL,12,Fconservation efforts around the world
OL,13,Fcan achieve.
OL,15,F"Wild giant otter populations are
OL,16,Ffacing enormous pressure from
OL,17,Fwidespread habitat loss and pollution
OL,18,Fin their freshwater ecosystems, so the
OL,19,Finternational conservation breeding
OL,20,Fprogramme has become a vital safety
OL,21,Fnet for the species.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775909467
OL,3,CZoo sees birth of otter triplets from
OL,4,Cone of world's most endangered species
OL,6,F"By maintaining healthy, genetically
OL,7,Fdiverse populations in conservation
OL,8,Fzoos like ours, while also supporting
OL,9,Fefforts to protect and restore
OL,10,Fhabitats in the wild, we're hopeful
OL,11,Fthat giant otters can thrive long into
OL,12,Fthe future."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
